{
  "stem": "4361.9",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, that's why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, I am also published author of a book called which does have to do a lot about the people of Sighet who came back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it is a historical novel based-- drawn on, on factual things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did a book on the partisan resistance, as I said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "is out of print now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was published in '79.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the book on the partisan-- the Jewish partisan resistance is called It has not yet been published.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, what I would like to say is this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "More or less, what I told the Pope last year when on April 7, as you may know, the Vatican for the first time in 50 years had a commemorative concert in the Vatican.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And among the many, many 7,000 or so dignitaries, bishops, cardinals, et cetera, 100 survivors were also invited by the Vatican, and I was among them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Pope was very gracious in giving a private interview to the 100 of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And each one-- and he spoke very movingly to us, saying something about how good it is to dwell in brotherhood in this house, which was a quote.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And how terrible it was what had happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, he said the right things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then every survivor went up and said something to the Pope.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when my turn came, I said to him that I am grateful to him for doing what he did by recognizing and commemorating this event because they, they-- there are those who deny that it ever happened.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that means that not only were-- was I a victim once, but I was vict-- I am victimized a second time by denying my first victimization.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
